Usage: get_snap_grid_info [-help] [-origin] [-pitch_x] [-pitch_y]
                          -type {manufacturing inst placement userDefine LayerTrack finfetInst finfetManufacturing finfetPlacement}

-help       # Prints out the command usage
-origin     # Specify to get the original point of grid. (bool, optional)
-pitch_x    # Specify to get the X-direction pitch of grid. (bool, optional)
-pitch_y    # Specify to get the Y-direction pitch of grid. (bool, optional)
-type {manufacturing inst placement userDefine LayerTrack finfetInst finfetManufacturing finfetPlacement}
            # Specify the grid type which you want to get info. (enum, required)